Text:
Great, great stuff.  These are the comics that turned me into a life-long Ditko fan.  I knew his work on Amazing Spider-man, which was very good, but he really out did himself on Doctor Strange.  It was the first time another dimension looked actually different.  Very creative stuff!

I already have all of these (in paper form too!) but thanks for the upload.
Are these just Dr. Strange, or do they have the Human Torch & Nick Fury stories too?
I've been meaning to chase these up for a while now. Thanks!

My share ratio has hit 9.6, so it's up to you all to keep seeding this for others to enjoy due to my limited bandwidth
Please keep it seeding!
